                    <div class="course-content">
                        <h2 class="course-title">Electrical VNS</h2>
                        <p class="course-description">Electrical Vagus Nerve Stimulation has become a remarkably widespread method of at-home stimulation of the Vagus Nerve, first as an implanted device, and in the last 5 years, as a popular handheld battery powered device.</p>
