                        <p class="course-description">Coming in more recently since 2017, and Sterling Cooley's rare discovery of the effectiveness of low-intensity Ultrasound on the Vagus Nerve, you will learn about readily available devices often times far more affordable, with less of the 'over-stimulating' effects of other methods.</p>
                        <a href="https://skool.com/vagus/ultrasound" class="course-button">Learn about Ultrasound VNS</a>
