                        <p class="course-description">Not all exercise is created equal! Explore how specific movements—like yoga flows, tai chi, and rhythmic cardio—stimulate the vagus nerve to reduce stress hormones and improve resilience. Includes guided routines for all fitness levels, plus how to avoid overtraining (a common vagus saboteur!). Transform workouts from draining to energizing with vagus-centric movement science.</p>
                        <a href="https://skool.com/vagus/movement" class="course-button">Move with Purpose</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

